{"view":"article","slug":"f2l-speffz-naming","category":"3x3","subcategory":null,"topDir":"3x3","title":{"en":"F2L Speffz Naming","zh":"F2L Speffz命名"},"content":{"en":"<p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/f2l-speffz-naming/en/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>F2L Speffz Naming</strong></p><p>Assume white cross. <a href=\"/tutorial/f2l\" class=\"see-also-link\" data-see-also=\"true\">F2L</a> speffz name can be represent as [white sticker of target slot] [white sticker of F2L corner] [F2L edge sticker which has front/back face color] [white sticker of open slots]. For multislotting, notate each pair separated by slashes. For standard F2L, one can skip the first letter V. </p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/f2l-speffz-naming/en/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/f2l-speffz-naming/en/image6.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/f2l-speffz-naming/en/image8.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/f2l-speffz-naming/en/image10.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/f2l-speffz-naming/en/image12.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>VJB or JB</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>WTF</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>WJQV</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>VCCUW</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>UKC/VJB</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>Standard F2L List</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><a id=\"_Hlk53168601\"></a><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/f2l-speffz-naming/en/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/f2l-speffz-naming/en/image14.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=